  Source:
    Title: Harijan
    Editor: Mohandas Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 6 April 1940
---
Faith is a function of the heart, It must be enforced by reason, The
two are not antagonistic as some think, The more intense one's faith is,
the more it whets one's reason, When faith becomes blind it dies.
